title: [1958] John Coltrane - Settin' The Pace (320kbps)
description:
Great 1958 album by John Coltrane. Includes artists such as Red Garland on piano, Paul Chambers on bass, & Arthur Taylor on drums. This was ripped from the remastered version. Quality is 320kbps.
